snippet.title: ALL WILL FALL - Official Announcement Trailer | Physics-Based Survival City Builder | Steam Games
snippet.description:
⚓ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2706020/ALL_WILL_FALL_PhysicsBased_Survival_City_Builder

WISHLIST & JOIN THE PLAYTEST ON STEAM NOW! 

* * * * * *
In this survival colony sim, build a tower city up to the sky and make sure it does not fall… literally. Master realistic physics-based construction mechanics, manage the needs of your people and make tough decisions as a leader of the last bastion of civilization amid the endless ocean.
